text.tspan: Want to build a custom pinball machine?

flowRoot.flowPara: Software for powering real pinball machines. 100% free. 100% open source.
- Buy or build a control system

text.tspan: Why use MPF as a software framework?

flowRoot.flowPara: - Support for LCD. DMD or segment displays
- Built-in support for almost all pinball mechanisms
- Build a machine with config files or in python code
